author: Trey Alston
title: DJ D-Nice And Michelle Obama Are Throwing A Virtual Voting Party
description: DJ D-Nice has collaborated with former first lady Michelle Obama for a virtual voting party during this time of social isolation. #CouchParty kicks off tonight at 6:30 p.m. ET.
